{"tid":390350,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有人說\"人的存在是享受，而不是捱苦\"，你同意嗎？試抒己見","createTime":"2017-09-07T04:46:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-16T05:40:25.000Z","uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0d77663c621963b0ff2c099027b2a4bb880a5d78","tid":390350,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T04:46:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n承上題<br />\n如果要你選擇吃下紅藥丸，去走一條相對困難而痛苦的路，去發現真相，或者吃下藍藥丸，去走一條相對舒適而平坦的路，活在無知當中，你會如何選擇？為什麼？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/07/124633_24438e4ad23f8f2fcdc871e87a13fbf1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F07%2F124633_24438e4ad23f8f2fcdc871e87a13fbf1.jpg&h=1a76cc82&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6e22cd5f0f2c0fe3f23d6782c7a4c55b7d2a6c79","tid":390350,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T04:49:09.000Z","msg":"真相係咩真相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37e23faaf4144118642b1ee21a4e4476e8363627","tid":390350,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T01:52:06.000Z","msg":"答左第一題先"},{"pid":"b9578e7bad5c5430bab9308b11bbf84c59ad738b","tid":390350,"uid":82542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:53:00.000Z","msg":"No"},{"pid":"da3098e2f4b902cd855e4e6e6326fb6be92fea7f","tid":390350,"uid":123012,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T04:13:32.000Z","msg":"藍藥丸，活在無知當中<br />\n<br />\n知道左真相就會有能力改變??<br />\n一路辛苦去堅持努力到最後的結果，只係得到左一個你改變唔到的事實<br />\n禁知道個真相有咩用??<br />\n<br />\n選條舒服的路起碼過程中享受過"},{"pid":"110bee5bd5a988ee897a4a661bdfd7b9592e2edd","tid":390350,"uid":121863,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T04:22:01.000Z","msg":"人的存在是為快樂，而不是著眼於痛苦"},{"pid":"410ebfee417ee0470c64716b1071f9db200323a7","tid":390350,"uid":108026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T04:23:45.000Z","msg":"matrix <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"641251770d4e33add8f68c231152004cd376b582","tid":390350,"uid":110832,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T04:25:54.000Z","msg":"戇鳩<br />\n舒服就要無知?<br />\n痛苦先有真相?"},{"pid":"5c7360b8f5a33c763e39bcadf78c9a9e00bae96f","tid":390350,"uid":33991,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T04:52:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戇鳩<br />\n舒服就要無知?<br />\n痛苦先有真相?</blockquote><br />\n個題目係咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你就on9"},{"pid":"f5129d2976353db20414a20f98c0c10fb99023ed","tid":390350,"uid":74778,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T04:55:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戇鳩<br />\n舒服就要無知?<br />\n痛苦先有真相?</blockquote><br />\n自古以來，無論邊一個國家既歷史都反映住愚民政策，鼓勵人管好自己既生計之後，就唔好再理一d政策上，甚至世界性既大是大非。<br />\n<br />\n你想行既路係平坦、舒適、狹隘、無知<br />\n<br />\n定係崎嶇、艱辛、遼闊、自由，又痛苦"},{"pid":"0cc3094ba488003ca1946b037863e0d7406cc02a","tid":390350,"uid":122211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T04:59:15.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"cda264a0a0374418e6cb13e0578bc06e2877f101","tid":390350,"uid":99048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T05:07:25.000Z","msg":"不如咁講<br />\n<br />\n你想做有錢而無知嘅北韓人<br />\n<br />\n定係想做知道自己國家有幾廢嘅金仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed5b3ae7f40013f63a2583b3ab7fb38eb07026c0","tid":390350,"uid":123907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T05:10:28.000Z","msg":"咩叫發現真相？咁如果真相就係你注定要受苦 咁點解要認清真相"},{"pid":"6e32a3aaf419c602f97981a1496b23af0dbe2e81","tid":390350,"uid":123907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T05:12:21.000Z","msg":"你又點define享受同捱苦？咁如果有人享受捱苦又算唔算捱苦？捱苦嘅過程唔痛苦又算唔算捱苦？"},{"pid":"45e1ee99c9e26bfb4a121ee06b487b0037b11bdc","tid":390350,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,